{
  "stem": "748.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- three weeks, I was by a microphone and explain what was it, how I was in-- I-- I-- they took me to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, she's not alive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Katalina Litkinska.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When they took me to jail.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother was already in-- they took her before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not in the jail.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They take her to Treblinka, to another concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Barbara, mine father arranged with a priest-- I didn't know even this-- that he should give care of the baby.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then they arranged-- when they-- when they took us, and I got the baby on mine arm, I should leave on the steps and run back.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is-- I don't know that they didn't-- they was blind, the SS, or something, that they don't see me running.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I left her on the step of the-- in the church.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was my father arrangement with the priest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He used to come every Friday for supper to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] he's a priest.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A priest.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the street, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Zamoiska. ?] But how the priest called-- the-- the church, he called, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In jail, I was about six, seven months, until they maked a transport to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The SS, if they wanted, they came, took every day another person.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you just hear a shot outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You wasn't a human being, at this time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You-- you [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They call us Jewish whore, Jewish this-- you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Very, very--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They took me, transport.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They make a big transport into Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Normal.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They tell-- tell us to go out from the jail.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we were, at the time, a couple hundred in big trucks.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
